sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant R as Route
    participant P as Pipeline
    participant B as Base cache
    participant K as Knowledge (RAG)
    participant A as AI client
    participant S as Signals
    participant O as Overlay
    C->>R: POST /api/reports
    R->>R: Zod-validate input
    R->>P: runReportPipeline
    P->>B: ensureReportBase(key)
    alt cache hit
        B-->>P: ready base
    else miss
        B->>K: retrieve knowledge (graceful-empty)
        B->>A: generateStructured (render, call, parse, retry once, log cost)
        A-->>B: validated advisory
    end
    P->>S: gather signals (concurrent, optional)
    P->>O: overlay if date is near (deterministic fallback)
    P-->>R: report + provenance
    R-->>C: 200 JSON
